ahhh im so excited. annas party is tomorrow and so is her birthday ((happy birthday)) and taylors party is on saturday. oh yeah and halloween is on monday! me kari erik and jenna are all gonna be people from the wizard of oz, possibly.


yesterday was the football game against banks at western. it was amazing, we got the winning touchdown in like the last 1.2 seconds of the game. sweetest game ive ever been to. all varsity guys, you had an awesome season. i cant wait until we cheer for you in high school

and to all the girls from cheerleading, we had a great season. im glad that was the team i was on for my last time cheering in middle school. i'll miss you all!!

ok im done with my speechy thing. lol. the canteen was today. they're all usually pretty gay. but this one was alright. lmao i danced with alex hays, what a cutie..... if you havent signed the petition for the formal eighth grade canteen, make sure you sign it.

if anyone is going to the gwen/black eyed peas concert and wants to take me i will love you forever <3

omg christmas is in like less than two months and my birthday is in a month and three days. i cant wait. me and hannah are gonna take snowboarding lessons!! haha. we will be awesome. 


ok so if you want to comment go ahead, not like anyone does anyways. 



lovee 
allie

geez i've never been so scared.. i thought i was gonna  die.
